                {
                    "__type__": "Note",
                    "fields": [
                        "When did SVB (Silicon Valley Bank) collapse?",
                        "<div>March 10, 2023</div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">On March 10, 2023, </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Silicon_Valley_Bank\">Silicon Valley Bank</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> (SVB) </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_failure\">failed</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> after a </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_run\">bank run</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, marking the </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_largest_bank_failures_in_the_United_States\">third-largest bank failure in United States history</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> and the largest since the </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2007%E2%80%932008_financial_crisis\">2007–2008 financial crisis</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">.</span><sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Collapse_of_Silicon_Valley_Bank#cite_note-1\">[1]</a></sup><sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Collapse_of_Silicon_Valley_Bank#cite_note-NYT-20230313-2\">[2]</a></sup><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> It was one of three bank failures, along with </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Silvergate_Bank\">Silvergate Bank</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> and </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Signature_Bank\">Signature Bank</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, in March 2023 in the United States.</span><br></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Ref: </span><font color=\"#202122\" face=\"sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Collapse_of_Silicon_Valley_Bank</span></font></div>"
