    "notes": [
        {
            "__type__": "Note",
            "fields": [
                "A {{c1::gunnysack}} is a large, simple bag made of rough material and traditionally used for carrying grain or vegetables<sup>1</sup>. It is also known as a gunny shoe, burlap sack, hessian sack or tow sack<sup>2</sup>.\n<br><img alt=\"picture of gunnysack\" src=\"gunnys_noun_004_1440.jpg\">",
                "<ol><li>https://dictionary.cambridge.org/us/dictionary/english/gunnysack</li><li>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gunny_sack<br></li></ol>"
            ],
            "guid": "EAAT$FE_ln",
            "note_model_uuid": "56671b6a-b205-11ef-9801-d0abd5c278c3",
            "tags": []
        },
        {
            "__type__": "Note",
            "fields": [
                "The year {{c1::46 BC}} is the {{c2::longest}} calendar year in recorded history. It had {{c3::445}} days and was nicknamed the {{c4::annus confusionis}} (“{{c5::Year of Confusion}}”).<br>",
                "Ref:- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/46_BC"
            ],
            "guid": "Id0{f6i`kB",
            "note_model_uuid": "56671b6a-b205-11ef-9801-d0abd5c278c3",
            "tags": []
        },
        {
            "__type__": "Note",
            "fields": [
                "The transistor was successfully demonstrated on {{c1::December 23, 1947::date}} at {{c2::Bell Laboratories::company}} in {{c3::Murray Hill, New Jersey::city, state}}. {{c2::Bell Labs::company}} was the research arm of {{c4::American Telephone and Telegraph (AT&amp;T)::company}}. The three individuals credited with the invention of the transistor were {{c5::William Shockley}}, {{c6::John Bardeen}} and {{c7::Walter Brattain}}.<br>",
                "Ref:- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_of_the_transistor"
            ],
            "guid": "l7E7k,ys3q",
            "note_model_uuid": "56671b6a-b205-11ef-9801-d0abd5c278c3",
            "tags": []
        },
        {
            "__type__": "Note",
            "fields": [
                "The word {{c1::bit}} is short for {{c2::binary digit}}.",
