            "tags": []
        },
        {
            "__type__": "Note",
            "fields": [
                "<div>The first effective measles vaccine was developed by {{c1::Dr. John F. Enders}}&nbsp;and licensed in {{c2::1963}}.<sup></sup><div></div></div><div><br></div><div>An improved and weaker measles vaccine was later developed by {{c3::Dr. Maurice Hilleman}}&nbsp;and began to be distributed in {{c4::1968}}.<sup></sup>&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>{{c5::Dr. Maurice Hilleman}} also developed the combined {{c6::MMR (measles, mumps, rubella)}} vaccine in {{c7::1971}}.</div>",
                ""
            ],
